AIF mentions you the five main reasons for visiting Israel.
Contradict the Holy Sites
Visit the Jordan River where Jesus was baptized.
It means that all who bathe in this river receive God’s blessing.
Galilee is the place where Jesus performed his miracles: the transformation of water into wine at a wedding feast, the going on the water, the calming of the sea tower and fishing.
