It is true that working with well-known singers has helped us, and we have also started to advertise actively for ourselves.
We have become aware that if you do something and you cannot see it outwardly, your own performance does not exist in a sense.
Moreover, thanks to the EU funding funds, we can afford good readers, high-quality equipment and so on.
