Some come to us with romantic ideas, and if they find that they have two times a week of sample, have to complete preparatory phases and spend a lot of time on concert trips, then the enthusiasm with many loses quickly.
That's how it works everywhere, in every band that wants to work seriously and achieve something.
The Tap Tap currently has twenty members.
